main event: Mr. Howard Snyder observed a dark rectangular-shaped object hovering over the Lehigh University campus in Bethlehem, Pennsylvania on January 6, 1967, for approximately 10 minutes.
interesting points: The object was estimated to be 30 to 40 feet in length,The object appeared metallic and silent,Several other residents reported similar sightings,The sighting took place at approximately 2100 hours,The case is listed as UNIDENTIFIED due to lack of corroborating evidence.
sighted object: one dark rectangular-shaped object in the sky
witness description: Mr. Howard Snyder, a resident of Bethlehem, Pennsylvania
